{"id": "1436542930528768122", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "札とか密約の「狂気増加」って何が増加しているんでしょうか？効果を実感したことがないので、誰か教えていただきたいです", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T02:28:44.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436548261962842134", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1419110621533704253", "author_name": "tuyu1ro._.1128", "author_bot": false, "content": "確か狂気解放したあとに\n狂気増加の分だけ狂気貰えるみたいな...\nそんな感じだったと思います！", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T02:49:55.428000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1425265631078645841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436542930528768122", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436558288518119690", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど！\n仮に狂気増加3.6の札を装備してボス戦で2回狂気解放したとしたら、狂気7.2が増加する....ということですね。\nありがとうございます！\n狂気増加はないものとして育成進めます！", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T03:29:45.945000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1419110621533704253"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436548261962842134", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436596591040532602", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂気増加はとても弱いです、悲しいね\nせめて札1枚で+20〜30くらい欲しい", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:01:57.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:02:40.863000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436597481789063168", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "試しに狂気密約を軽く作ってみたら元の値から2とか3とかしか増えてなくて泣きました。", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:05:30.349000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436604097653510244", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "増加値が低すぎるのよ", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:31:47.694000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436604216494915627", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "遺物で+50とか盛れるくせに", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:32:16.028000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436604777806041089", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "運営としては狂気を付与できるもしくは自家発電が可能なキャラクターで、毎ターン狂気解放が撃ててしまう状況を恐れているのかなーとは思っております。", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:34:29.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["438289046993633281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436604216494915627", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436604993007521923", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "札も密約も最大まで尖らせた狂気ビルド気にはなりますけどねー。", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:35:21.163000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436606190015483976", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "深海で怒涛時+を合わせるのが1番やれる\nあれだけで+50なので", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:40:06.552000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1032734003712774174"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436604993007521923", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436606556929130548", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "えー！深海ってそんな盛れるんですね‼️👀狂気の回転率だと狂魔がTOPだと思っておりました。怒涛って事は深海キャラだと一律50ずつ盛れちゃうのかなー？", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:41:34.031000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["438289046993633281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436606190015483976", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436606667037999205", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "密約も札も1しかないからそのキャラだけだね", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:42:00.283000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1032734003712774174"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "😊", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1436606556929130548", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436607223957557362", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "触腕増加系のサポに合わせるのが良さそう❓", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:44:13.063000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436608354351976510", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "深海普段つかわないけど、深海をただの盾やサポートのつもりで組み入れた編成とかの方が活かせそう", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:48:42.570000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436608758783410297", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "分かりみ！触らんすぎて勝手にタコの足が増えてくな〜くらいの感想しかない。", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:50:18.994000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436608923200258139", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1032734003712774174", "author_name": "aku08158", "author_bot": false, "content": "それで知らないうちに「え〜なんか減ってる〜〜なんでぇ？？」になってます。✋", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T06:50:58.194000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1436618334832558181", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "378233092801953792", "author_name": "masayan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "やっぱトゥルーにつけるのが一番良いかなって思います。戦闘初めに打って怒涛解放して～って連続でできます。", "timestamp": "2025-11-08T07:28:22.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "‼️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
